  "Description": {
    "English": "An augmentation for the colossal hyperdrive engine of an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">interstellar freighter</span>.<br><br>Quantum resonation improves the robustness of the drive during FTL travel, granting the ability to leap to stars previously out of reach.",
